---
title: One-Pot Chicken Alfredo with Parmesan, Fresh Oregano, and Broccoli
description: Just when we thought our favourite Alfredo dish couldn’t get any better, this one-pot game-changer came along. Cook the pasta in its sauce for a creamy dream come true - not to mention an infinitely easier clean-up.
